member.summary: Attempts to add buffs in array order.
member.param:
Amount of buffs to apply, this can be used to have a priority system.
For example, Crimson and Corruption Hellfire set this parameter to 1. So when they are inflicted and an enemy is immune, it will try to inflict Hellfire as Corruption/Crimson Hellfire failed to be applied.Anything below 0 means it will try to apply all buffs.
